#: content/community/calendar/2026/grazerlinuxtag.md:18
msgid ""
"Grazer Linuxtage is an annual conference around Open source software and "
"hardware. KDE will have a stand there and you can meet some of the "
"developers."
msgstr ""

#: content/community/calendar/2026/megasprint.md:0
